snippet.title: Ants Took My Eyeball - Trailer 2024 (demo available!)
snippet.description:
Ants Took My Eyeball is coming in April 2024! Play the demo and wishlist: https://steampowered.com/app/1627890

Ants Took My Eyeball is an upcoming 4-player local co-op roguelite action platformer.

Steam: https://steampowered.com/app/1627890
Twitter: https://twitter.com/antstookmyeye
Website: https://antstookmyeyeball.com
Press kit: https://antstookmyeyeball.com/press
